cff-version: 1

message: >-
  If you use Quantiles, please cite it as below.

title: "Quantiles: Local-first AI evaluation infrastructure"

abstract: >-
  Quantiles is an open-source, local-first CLI and SDK toolchain for
  running AI evaluation workflows, recording runs, inspecting sample-level
  results, comparing regressions, and supporting coding-agent evaluation
  workflows.

type: software

authors:
  - name: "Quantiles Contributors"

repository-code: "https://github.com/quantiles-evals/quantiles-os"

url: "https://quantiles.io"

license: Apache-2.0

keywords:
  - "AI evaluation"
  - "AI benchmarking"
  - "evaluation infrastructure"
  - "LLM evaluation"
  - "agent evaluation"
